lead_paragraph: England striker Danny Welbeck sustained a knee injury in Arsenal's Premier League match at Manchester City on Sunday, raising doubts about his availability for next month's European Championship.

headline.print_headline: England's Welbeck a Doubt for Euro 2016 With Knee Injury
